---
title: Steak 'Frites' with Creamy Horseradish Sauce
description: We're trading in the traditional spuds for seasonal root veggies in our fun take on steak frites. Served alongside a tangy horseradish sauce, we think you'll love it.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/steak-frites-2d3aad5b.jpg
